reviews: [{'Comment': "Must be good, second pair I've bought after leafing the first pair in the back of a TukTuk. Easy to put in your ears and then very, very comfy. reviews: [{'Comment': 'It blocks the noise well, so you feel very comfortable while talking on the phone and listening to music. Battery life is very ideal. ProductName: JBL Clip 4 Portable Speaker with Bluetooth
reviews:
[{'Comment': "I've been riding with these for six months, and am very happy with them.

The audio quality isn't perfect, but this comes with the HUGE benefit of being able to hear what is going on around you. The funny thing is that if you wear earplugs with these (or stick your fingers in your ears!), the audio quality will match most in-ear headphones.

Battery life is very good. I have used them for more than five hours, so it seems that the claimed life of 6 hours is realistic.", 'Source': 'REI', 'CommentDate': '2022-01-24', 'rating': 4.0, 'max_rating': 5.0, 'average_rating': 0}]

reviews: [{'Comment': 'I have had this laptop for about 3 weeks now and I have no complaints. It works great for everything that I need it for. This includes light computing load activities like communicating with my clients and team via Slack and Email, and also for heavier load activities like editing and designing websites on WebFlow and Editor X.\n\nAnother nice surprise was that although this laptop has a 2.2k screen, it can connect to a 4k monitor and present a 4k resolution.', 'Source': 'Lenovo', 'CommentDate': '2022-10-11', 'rating': 5.0, 'max_rating': 5.0, 'average_rating': 0}]

ProductName: Samsung Galaxy Tab S7+ 8GB, 256GB, 12.4" Super AMOLED, Black
reviews: [{'Comment': 'Awesome laptop (with a price to match), very capable and mobile for a 16" device. It\'s handling all I need - Web dev and integration, light gaming, video and photo editing. Flash design and the corner ports are handy. I am abit scared to scratch it but it\'s turning out to be strong. Fast charging, good battery life and power saving mode, amazing screen; it\'s checking all the boxes for me.', 'Source': 'PB Tech', 'CommentDate': '2023-03-10', 'rating': 4.0, 'max_rating': 5.0, 'average_rating': 0}]

reviews: [{'Comment': 'Battery life is amazing. Design and quality is great. Price is unbeatable but sensors are not accurate at all and I ended up stop using them after one week of struggle. reviews:
[{'Comment': 'Controller is an official Sony product. It is perfect.

The product page for this combo states (regarding the charging dock):
"And with the DualSense charging station, you can dock up to two DualSense wireless controllers so you can stay in the game and be ready to face your friends at a moment's notice. From Sony."

I'm sure it probably works fine, but it is definitely not FROM SONY. It is a brand called Gamefitz.', 'Source': 'QVC', 'CommentDate': '2023-11-02', 'rating': 4.0, 'max_rating': 5.0, 'average_rating': 0}]

reviews:
[{'Comment': 'The Sony WH-CH250 wireless Bluetooth on ear headphones truly is value for money, with the 50hours of nonstop clear and powerful music blasting away in the gym, at home or at work, the headphones are really a good buy,

Charging is also not a problem with the updated USB-C charge port, the headphones are giving “luxury” with some change to spare compared to the prices of other brands,

Very much worth considering', 'Source': 'Takealot', 'CommentDate': '2024-02-13', 'rating': 5.0, 'max_rating': 5.0, 'average_rating': 0}]

ProductName: Harman Kardon Onyx Studio 8 Portable Stereo Bluetooth Speaker, Black
reviews: [{'Comment': 'I purchased a couple weeks ago and am super content with it. It’s perfect for its size. I read some reviews beforehand and one said “the battery didn’t last more than 2hrs,” but I did a full charge beforehand and played it for over 4hrs ++ and it didn’t die (but decided to charge before it actually did).\nThe 1 thing i will say I don’t like, is the power button on the side, I have bumped it a few times by accident and it turned off. That’s it!', 'Source': 'Verizon Wireless', 'CommentDate': '2022-08-01', 'rating': 5.0, 'max_rating': 5.0, 'average_rating': 4.01}]

ProductName: Harman Kardon Onyx Studio 8 Portable Stereo Bluetooth Speaker, Black
reviews: [{'Comment': "I already had two JBL Flip 4's but I wanted to give the Flip 6 a try. Not only can it play louder than the Flip 4 i also love that the eq can be adjusted through the JBL app. I can't stand to listen to anything over my phone speakers now, i always carry this JBL Flip 6!", 'Source': 'Crutchfield', 'CommentDate': '2023-10-18', 'rating': 5.0, 'max_rating': 5.0, 'average_rating': 4.01}]

ProductName: Harman Kardon Onyx Studio 8 Portable Stereo Bluetooth Speaker, Black
reviews: [{'Comment': 'Wow this Bose Pro S1 is a powerhouse in a little box. It truly delivers amazing sound and bass. I’m going to purchase another to complete my setup for small venues. It’s small compact and the battery lasts long! I love the bluetooth and with the Bose app I can control it remotely from my phone.', 'Source': 'American Musical', 'CommentDate': '2023-11-29', 'rating': 5.0, 'max_rating': 5.0, 'average_rating': 4.01}]

reviews: [{'Comment': 'Product is excellent best too woofer performance outstanding', 'Source': 'LG', 'CommentDate': '2023-08-11', 'rating': 5.0, 'max_rating': 5.0, 'average_rating': 4.01}]

ProductName: Harman Kardon Onyx Studio 8 Portable Stereo Bluetooth Speaker, Black
reviews: [{'Comment': 'I bought these to replace a pair of Sony WF-1000XM4 earbuds. The Bose Ultra Quiet are superior in every way. The for is more customisable, with both interchangeable tips and bands, they are more comfortable and secure in use and the noise cancelling is way better than Sony.Sound quality is excellent and the immersion setting truly impressive. These are probably the best wireless earbuds on the market right now.', 'Source': 'World Wide Stereo', 'CommentDate': '2023-12-12', 'rating': 5.0, 'max_rating': 5.0, 'average_rating': 4.01}]

ProductName: Harman Kardon Onyx Studio 8 Portable Stereo Bluetooth Speaker, Black
reviews: [{'Comment': 'Bose has done it again! The design and look of the Quiet Comfort Ultra Headphones are perhaps the most aesthetically pleasing of any of the long line of Bose over the ear products. The fit is comfortable and the headphones are so light that it does not feel like you have them on. You have to spend some time with these headphones to find the sound that works for you.', 'Source': 'Bose', 'CommentDate': '2023-10-21', 'rating': 5.0, 'max_rating': 5.0, 'average_rating': 4.13}]

ProductName: Harman Kardon Onyx Studio 8 Portable Stereo Bluetooth Speaker, Black
reviews: [{'Comment': 'Purchased about 60 days ago. Had it professionally installed and it does sound good. However, we are having problems with it staying connected. It will turn off for no reason while watching and it will NOT reconnect. We\'ve found the "easiest" fix is to unplug and reboot it. reviews: [{'Comment': "Bought this for use with Ikea Symfonisk bookshelf speakers as surrounds. Connected to Xbox Series X. Great little setup for gaming. reviews: [{'Comment': 'I spend most of my day in virtual meetings and wanted something that would allow me to be away from my desk but still have good audio quality. These ear buds have been great. reviews: [{'Comment': 'I have used mine almost daily, for above 1:1, for about 2 years. reviews:
[{'Comment': 'The 3 star rating is an average between a device that meets 98 percent of its claims but fails miserably at one of them.

ProductName: Sennheiser Momentum True Wireless 3 Earbuds
reviews: [{'Comment': 'this speaker rocks as a little box it packs a heck of a punch. i love that the mics automatically connect wirelessly and initially one is provided with batteries (which will ultimately have to be replaced) however if i use the mics sparingly i trust that they can last long enough and to be safe, i shall also carry extra batteries in the event the need arises. my next action is to get a carrying case so its easier to carry around on the should versus using my hands.', 'Source': "Sam's Club", 'CommentDate': '2023-09-04', 'rating': 5.0, 'max_rating': 5.0, 'average_rating': 4.02}]

ProductName: Sennheiser Momentum True Wireless 3 Earbuds
reviews: [{'Comment': 'I spend most of my day in virtual meetings and wanted something that would allow me to be away from my desk but still have good audio quality. These ear buds have been great. They are comfortable and come with the alternate silicone tips so that you can adjust them for best fit. The storage box is a nice touch and makes charging easy. There is an app available for download but you can skip that and just pair via Bluetooth.', 'Source': 'Staples', 'CommentDate': '2022-05-19', 'rating': 5.0, 'max_rating': 5.0, 'average_rating': 4.02}]

ProductName: Sennheiser Momentum True Wireless 3 Earbuds
reviews: [{'Comment': "I was pleasantly surprised of the buds performance, sound is clear and punchy. The case is ridiculously light to such an extent I thought it must be ridiculously small. It's perfect for varied listening tasks. Very clear on phone calls, worked great for Teams meetings. Sony buds punch way above price point and plastic reused from ocean dumps make you feel you're helping great about cleaning up our amazing planet. There is no regrets just rewards.", 'Source': 'Crutchfield', 'CommentDate': '2023-02-10', 'rating': 5.0, 'max_rating': 5.0, 'average_rating': 3.87}]

ProductName: Sennheiser Momentum True Wireless 3 Earbuds
reviews: [{'Comment': 'If you have ever thought about getting airpods, stop, buy these instead. Why settle for the mediocre quality of apple when you can have these instead. Zero complaints for me, but that is expected from such an elite brand.', 'Source': 'Amazon', 'CommentDate': '2023-12-09', 'rating': 5.0, 'max_rating': 5.0, 'average_rating': 3.87}]

ProductName: Sennheiser Momentum True Wireless 3 Earbuds
reviews: [{'Comment': 'It’s big and heavy and one would think it would be loud with super bass but it’s really not impressive. reviews:
[{'Comment': "I've had this projector for about 6 months now and while it produces a decent image, it is not without its problems:

reviews: [{'Comment': "Excellent pairing with the Sony A7c. Shooting with a prime is so much fun, it forces you to be creative to frame the shot. But with a full sensor camera like the A7c, if you didn't quite get the shot framed perfectly, you can crop it later without any degradation to make the composition just right. The autofocus is fast and accurate, and there is no hunting. The bokeh with the 1.8 aperture is dreamy.", 'Source': 'Crutchfield', 'CommentDate': '2020-12-15', 'rating': 5.0, 'max_rating': 5.0, 'average_rating': 0}]

ProductName: Nikon Z8 Mirrorless Camera Body Only
reviews: [{'Comment': 'I love this lens as I bought it for obviously its Macro pedigree but also as a tack sharp (hate that term but it is) portrait lens. The contrast, bokeh and overall image quality is just unparalleled in my experience. Coming to think of it, I dont even notice any drop off even wide open. Having very recently left the Leica Rangefinder world (had a 35mm f2 and 90mm f2 APO) I can honestly say that the build quality is akin to those lenses.', 'Source': 'Imaging Resource', 'CommentDate': '2020-07-20', 'rating': 4.0, 'max_rating': 5.0, 'average_rating': 0}]

ProductName: Nikon Z8 Mirrorless Camera Body Only
reviews: [{'Comment': "This lens will allow you to take ridiculously sharp photos. The bokeh is as sweet as the 24mm focal length allows. It's not a macro lens, but focusing distance is far shorter than most non-macro lenses, so you can get pretty darn close to subject and get even blurrier backgrounds. If you rely on JPGs, the colors out of the box are very nice. And best of all, this thing is light so weight is pretty much a non-factor when carrying stuff all day.", 'Source': 'B&H Photo', 'CommentDate': '2019-06-03', 'rating': 5.0, 'max_rating': 5.0, 'average_rating': 4.07}]

ProductName: Nikon Z8 Mirrorless Camera Body Only
reviews: [{'Comment': "If you want a physical photo camera, this is the way to go! It's light, easy to use, and every photo turns out really well. If you want to get into physical photography and you don't have a printer, this is a wonderful starting point!", 'Source': 'The Exchange', 'CommentDate': '2023-05-10', 'rating': 5.0, 'max_rating': 5.0, 'average_rating': 4.07}]

ProductName: Nikon Z8 Mirrorless Camera Body Only
reviews: [{'Comment': 'I bought this lens last week for me canon EOS R and I must say after watching many talking head videos i was starting to regret the purchase before it arrived. Now that I have it and have had the chance to use it all I can say is wow. It is an incredibly small lens on the R and is very discrete. The image quality is sharp and amazing for both portraits and landscape. I think this is a must have lens its small and sharp. I do not at all regret this purchase.', 'Source': 'Canon', 'CommentDate': '2021-03-04', 'rating': 5.0, 'max_rating': 5.0, 'average_rating': 4.07}]

ProductName: Nikon Z8 Mirrorless Camera Body Only
reviews: [{'Comment': 'Bought this predominately for my Z6 and to take photos of my kids. Very sharp. Great for video too', 'Source': 'Crutchfield', 'CommentDate': '2020-05-03', 'rating': 5.0, 'max_rating': 5.0, 'average_rating': 4.07}]

ProductName: Nikon Z8 Mirrorless Camera Body Only
reviews: [{'Comment': "Value that you get from this camera and lens kit is amazing. It's a compact size that delivers serious image quality on the form factor that allows you to take the camera anywhere and be discreet. Also because I have the black and silver version it looks like an old-school camera and people immediately write you off and don't pay any attention to you places where are you may not be welcomed with a large professional camera. You can fly under the radar with this thing.", 'Source': 'District Camera', 'CommentDate': '2023-07-27', 'rating': 5.0, 'max_rating': 5.0, 'average_rating': 4.07}]

reviews: [{'Comment': "I really like this camera as it my first real buy.
